{"tid":1839104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港人條命真。矝貴］大家必須歧視排斥所有不佩戴口罩人仕","createTime":"2020-01-24T09:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T00:12:23.000Z","uid":124859,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0b940d3ada3c3583b712c0b852a6291a6e7633cd","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:28:45.000Z","msg":"至今岀街都仲有超過半數人冇戴口罩<br />\n特別D廢中廢老 新移民<br />\n佢地條命賤過地底泥一件事 好心咪撚拖埋我地落水啦<br />\n香港人條命真心好矜貴<br />\n班廢中廢老最中意上大陸叫雞<br />\n趕住拖喼上大陸團圓<br />\n快d攬撚住一起死啦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n所以，大家要由日常生活做起<br />\n歧視所有不佩戴口罩既畜牲<br />\n<br />\n係街一見到d畜牲就要誇張式彈開9丈遠<br />\n要奏眉啤實佢地，手作狀遮口鼻<br />\n表現絕對的歧視同排斥！！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不戴口罩=帶菌者</span></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c84b107f0a08329bf561bece9ee39543f8dfb06a","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:29:34.000Z","msg":"不戴口罩=帶菌者"},{"pid":"4e40c7d1ea9bd97235e1c14a6f70b0b1ccc630e3","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新一年 我靚女一名祝願：<br />\n香港獨立 唯一岀路<br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></span>"},{"pid":"2090d7e9af447f75423a464d1d2108e4a0908b2c","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:31:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"189d2568667f88d401dc2938b793c7a36a676563","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab74d92e3889cfe307f3531448a539dde36399be","tid":1839104,"uid":311566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T09:31:42.000Z","msg":"支持同響應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c245488302ffa04382713dec2bfa5b2e716380","tid":1839104,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24